<p>
<note n="0301001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0301001">依提伽，先植大菩提樹之日，來大精舍之摩魯毘耶帝須與摩訶哂陀兩長老之間交談之傳說，為刻於金牒之古傳說。</note>
<note n="0303002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0303002">在協會本，於此之上有「信士！今汝亦行此之道」之半偈，隨以下錫蘭本之半偈為齟齬。</note>
<note n="0303003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0303003">上之九偈參照。</note>
<note n="0303004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0303004">五-八偈以下參照。</note>
</p>
